    "text": [
        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "My name is Kajol Dave and I have had a savings bank account with the RBL bank at the Ahmedabad branch  ( Account number: 70005637896585) for the last five years. I am writing to express my dissatisfaction with receiving this letter for the reason of being overdrawn. I would like to inform you that this detail is wrong because have not withdrawn any amount for a long time.",
        "As RBL bank has provided good services to their customers. Moreover, yesterday, I received the letter from the bank and it is showing that have to pay the penalty of $70 against the withdrawal exceeding the amount. The information is incorrect because I have recently deposited the amount of money of $400 to maintain the minimum balance of this account and do not need to charge any amount from my account.",
        "I would request you to recheck the information and provide the confirmation in my registered email address to ensure that no charges will be taken from the savings account.",
        "I look forward to your quick response.",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Kajol Dave"
